             				</origPlace></creation><langUsage><language ident="de-x-enh" source="http://medieval-plants.org/mps-daten/inhalt/">Franconian</language></langUsage></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body xml:space="preserve"><div type="household" xml:lang="de-x-enh" n="2" xml:id="b5.2"> <foreign xml:lang="lat">ad faciendum</foreign> <ingredient en="sloe" commodity="Q12059685">schleen</ingredient> <dish en="pickle" commodity="Q1503784">kumpost</dish> <title key="Sloe pickles"><ingredient en="sloe" commodity="Q12059685">Schleen</ingredient> <dish en="pickle" commodity="Q1503784">kumpost</dish></title> macht man also eyn virtel <ingredient en="sloe" commodity="Q12059685">schleen</ingredient> vnde .200. <ingredient en="medlar" commodity="Q3092517">nespeln</ingredient> vnde .50. <ingredient en="pear" commodity="Q13099586">regels bern</ingredient> ader me vnde laß dy <ingredient en="pear" commodity="Q13099586">regels bern</ingredient> ober syeden als das sy eynen guten wal tun vnde wan das geschicht so nement eyn <tool en="vat" commodity="Q38942">kobel</tool> vnd legent dan von erst eyn lege <ingredient en="medlar" commodity="Q3092517">nespeln</ingredient> vnde dan eyne lege <ingredient en="sloe" commodity="Q12059685">schleen</ingredient> vnde dan <ingredient en="pear" commodity="Q13099586">bern</ingredient> dar zwschen vnd wan es gar geleyt wirt so neymdan <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honig</ingredient> vnde suße <ingredient en="wine" commodity="Q282">win</ingredient> dar noch daz er vil <dish en="puree" commodity="Q636056" ana="comparison">muß</dish> sin vnde sydent daz <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honig</ingredient> vnde den <ingredient en="wine" commodity="Q282">win</ingredient> vndereynander vnde laßent dy <ingredient en="pear broth" commodity="Q110611287">bru</ingredient> ober nocht sten das sy wol kalt werde vnd gaß dy <ingredient en="pear broth" commodity="Q110611287">brue</ingredient> dan dar ober vnde deckent es zuo des <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honiges</ingredient> vnde dez <ingredient en="wine" commodity="Q282">wyns</ingredient> salglich vil sin Dy <ingredient en="medlar" commodity="Q3092517">meßpeln</ingredient> solkent <pb xml:id="B5_047r" n="047r"/> harte sin Dy <ingredient en="sloe" commodity="Q12059685">schleyn</ingredient> sal der ryffe gebißen han </div></body></text></TEI>